# 2050 Fashion Brand - Cursor Rules

## Project Context
This is a high-end sustainable fashion brand called "2050" built on Shopify.

## Shopify Development Guidelines
- Use Shopify Liquid templating language for theme development
- Follow Shopify theme best practices and conventions
- Maintain accessibility standards (WCAG 2.1 AA)
- Optimize for performance (Core Web Vitals)
- Ensure mobile-first responsive design

## Code Style
- Use semantic HTML5
- Follow BEM naming convention for CSS classes
- Use modern JavaScript (ES6+)
- Maintain consistent indentation (2 spaces)

## Sustainability Focus
- Optimize images and assets for performance
- Minimize JavaScript bundle size
- Use efficient CSS (avoid unnecessary animations)
- Consider carbon footprint in design decisions

## File Organization
- Keep theme files organized in standard Shopify structure
- Use snippets for reusable components
- Use sections for customizable page elements
- Maintain clean separation of concerns

